---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Overview
description: "Learn about court mediation in Florida — program types, fees, statewide trends, and useful resources."
---

<article class="overview-page">
  <h1>Court Mediation in Florida — Overview</h1>

  <section class="overview-intro">
    <h2>What is Court Mediation in Florida?</h2>
    <p>{{ overview.intro }}</p>
  </section>

  <section class="overview-programs">
    {{ overview.program_types | markdownify | safe }}
  </section>

  <section class="overview-trends">
    {{ overview.trends | markdownify | safe }}
  </section>

  <section class="overview-links">
    <h2>Useful External Links</h2>
    <ul class="external-links">
      {% for link in overview.external_links %}
      <li><a href="{{ link.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ link.label }}</a></li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <p class="last-updated">Last updated: {{ overview.last_updated }}</p>
</article>
